# Getting Started with Yfinance

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:yfinance, path: "/Users/akoutmos/Documents/opensource/yfinance"},
  {:kino_vega_lite, "~> 0.1.10"},
  {:kino, "~> 0.12.0"}
])
```

## Get Historical Data

To get historical data for a stock from Yahoo! Finance®, you can

```elixir
{:ok, data_frame} =
  Yfinance.Ticker.history("aapl", Date.shift(Date.utc_today(), month: -12), Date.utc_today())

Kino.DataTable.new(data_frame)
```
